title: [A Flash Of Strength, Additions]
description: Woven from silk, a soiled tapestry hangs from the wall, its once-brilliant design faded with age.  Shelves line the crude walls, their lengths filled with a wide variety of helms.  Bits and pieces of armor accessories are stacks inside an iron-bound trunk.
